title: Kaleo Discography EAC - FLAC
description:
My second torrent on this website here and I'm more than happy to share this gem with the whole community :D

This includes Kaleo's first album named Kaleo and 4 of their singles released so far in CD Quality!!! (FLAC)

The album CD took a long time to find, but was able to buy it from some icelandic music shop online and had to wait about a month for it to fly over here, but it was definitely worth the wait.

Ripped with Exact Audio Copy V1.1 the quality percentage of the tracks are mostly 100%, with some 99.9%, but NOT ANY LOWER! (EAC logs included)

Took the time to do the tags properly and as a bonus, HI-RES SCANS of every image that was in this album.

The 4 singles are all bought from Qobuz and also include the cover art.

P.S. I just saw them live recently and they played like 4-5 new songs. They were all awesome, so definitely something to look forward too. (A bit of a downer side from the merch they were selling, was that they didn't have their first album a.k.a Kaleo, which would have been awesome for all the other people there).

P.P.S. I tried to get the album signed, but they weren't doing autographs :(

Enjoy the release!!! And please show feedback through comments on my second upload :)
